f=ts(df$Price,frequency=12)
corn_month=aggregate(f,FUN=mean)
corn_month=ts(corn_month,start = c(2010,6),frequency = 12)
plot(corn_month)

a=decompose(corn_month,"additive")
plot(a)

plot(a$seasonal[1:12],ty="l")

hw=HoltWinters(corn_month,seasonal = c("multiplicative"))
